column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.cModelMag_g, p.cModelMag_r, p.cModelMag_i,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  i.d4#_n, i.d4#_n_err,  g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecIndx AS i ON i.specobjid = s.specobjid  JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE  s.class = &&&  AND p.cModelMag_r < #
